  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p707049/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201406/c4eb420a-edc1-4d02-9c43-969dc82f4ef1.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\">《英闻天天译》</a></strong></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">是一档沪江部落的原创翻译互动节目（</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128,0,128); line-height: 1.8em;\"><a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/item/957908/\"><strong>戳去参与节目&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></a></span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">），主持人提供翻译参考文本，对大家递交的翻译作品进行点评，和大家共同进步！本期节目选取的是关于</span>经济影响文学<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family: verdana, helvetica; color: rgb(51,51,51); line-height: 28px;\">一则英文报道，让我们一起在翻译中关注</span><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">。</font></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://img.washingtonpost.com/news/the-intersect/wp-content/uploads/sites/32/2014/09/emma.jpg\" /></span></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px;\"><span style=\"border-top: 0px; font-family: verdana, helvetica; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; margin: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\"><strong>SUMMARY：</strong></span></span></span></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<span>本周互联网假消息：基本上一切都是假的。</span></div>\n<div>\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">CONTENT：</strong></div>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t4chan did not threaten to leak Emma Watson&rsquo;s <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/nude\" target=\"_blank\">nude</a>s. Like a lame Internet <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sequel\" target=\"_blank\">sequel</a> to Christopher Nolan&rsquo;s &ldquo;Inception,&rdquo; the big Emma Watson Nude Leak of 2014 was basically &hellip; a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/hoax\" target=\"_blank\">hoax</a> within a hoax within a hoax. (Where to begin?!) Essentially, a marketing company called Rantic posed as users of the infamous, oft-misunderstood message board 4chan, claiming they&rsquo;d leak stolen photos of Watson at midnight on Sept. 24 in retaliation for a feminist speech she made at the United Nations.<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhen the appointed hour came, of course, Rantic revealed that there were no pictures and no 4chan <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/conspiracy\" target=\"_blank\">conspiracy</a>. In fact, there isn&rsquo;t even a Rantic Marketing! The &ldquo;company,&rdquo; which swore it was hired by Hollywood publicists, is actually just another front for a group of Internet <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/prankster\" target=\"_blank\">prankster</a>s called Social VEVO. To quote the Guardian&rsquo;s James Ball in an excellent essay on the debacle, &ldquo;the Internet is eating itself.&rdquo; Basically.</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0,100,0);\"><strong>【沪江英语小编】</strong></span>大家在查看主持人提供的翻译版本前，可以先自己进行尝试翻译练习，只有在不断的翻译中翻译能力才能有所提升哦！<br />\n\t轻松注册沪江，马上参与<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>【英闻天天译】</strong></a>节目练翻译&rarr;<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/810ca373cf4442a188b39dd8ff64425f.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>本期节目参考译文：</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(128,128,128);\">（参考译文由该节目主持人提供，仅供参考，欢迎大家讨论）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文1：</strong></span></p>\n<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\">4chan网站并没有威胁泄露艾玛&middot;沃森的裸照。就像给克里斯托弗&middot;诺兰的《盗梦空间》狗尾续貂一样，2014年艾玛&middot;沃森的裸照泄露事件基本上是&hellip;&hellip;一场连环骗局。（搞不清楚始作俑者了）从本质上讲，一个名为&ldquo;兰蒂克（疯狂）&rdquo;的营销公司，冒充臭名昭著的、常常发布小道消息的4chan网站用户，声称他们将于9月24日深夜发布所窃得的沃森的照片，目的是为了报复其在联合国发表的女权主义演讲。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t当然，到了约定的时间，兰蒂克公司公布消息，照片和4chan的阴谋都是不存在的。事实上，连兰蒂克营销公司都是假的！这家自称受雇于好莱坞公关人员的&ldquo;公司&rdquo;，实际上只是被称为&ldquo;社交VEVO&rdquo;的互联网恶作剧者们的一个幌子。总的说来，借用《卫报》詹姆斯&middot;鲍尔关于这一乱象所写的一篇精彩文章中的话，&ldquo;互联网正在自我毁灭。&rdquo;</span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"color: #000;\"><strong>参考译文2：</strong></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"replyview red\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span style=\"color: #000;\"><span style=\"color: #000;\">4chan (外国的综合性讨论网站)并没有威胁说要放艾玛`沃特森的裸照。就像是一个如同盗梦空间般的蹩脚的互联网骗局。艾玛`沃特森大量裸照外泄这件事完全是一个骗局中的骗局（哪里开始？！）。事实上，是一家叫做RANTIC的营销公司9月24日深夜在声名狼藉的4chan平台上声称他们将发布沃特森被偷的照片，以此报复她在美国做的一场女权演讲。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t当然，约定时间到的时候，RANTIC透露他们手中并没有所谓的照片也并非4chan的合谋。事实上，这甚至不是一场RANTIC的营销秀。这家辩称自己雇佣于好莱坞公关的&ldquo;公司&rdquo;实际上不过是另一个名为社交VEVO的网络恶作剧团体打出的幌子。引用卫报詹姆斯鲍尔在一篇关于奔溃的优秀文章中所写，&ldquo;互联网正在吞噬他自己。&rdquo;从根本上来说是这样的。</span></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15399/item/957908/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0);\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p707049/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href