  "description": "<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Verdana, 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.8em;\">noticeable.</span><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: verdana, helvetica; text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" rel=\"nofollow\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201405/2b3a665f-5545-4fca-a30c-dd8c4ee997c0.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" target=\"_blank\" /></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t国民女婿十大标准新鲜出炉，是不是看傻眼了，倍感亚历山大!!<br />\n\t凭借《媳妇的美好时代》、《咱们结婚吧》等多部热播剧赢得&ldquo;国民女婿&rdquo;称号的黄海波前些日嫖娼被抓，这是继文章出轨后又一爆炸性新闻。<br />\n\t但是，奇怪的是，网友们竟然批评的少，狂赞的多!不少粉丝发声力挺黄海波，不少网友认为：第一，他没结婚。第二，他没女朋友。第三，他也没男朋友。他只是付费让一个女性做了她的临时女友，仅此而已。<br />\n\t同时，有主张&ldquo;嫖娼合法化&rdquo;者，从制度层面对此案提出质疑，认为黄海波嫖娼只是一个正常男人的正常生理需求的释放。如此&ldquo;芝麻小事&rdquo;被曝光，被指黄海波幕后没有关系，所以得罪了某些权势，这些评论把黄海波看作是弱势势力。</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t1. Do you agree with the idea of legalizing the action of <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/patronizing\" target=\"_blank\">patronizing</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/prostitute\" target=\"_blank\">prostitutes</a> in China?<br />\n\t2. In your eyes, what kind of man can be called &quot;China's <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/son-in-law\" target=\"_blank\">son-in-law</a>&quot;?<br />\n\t3. DIY one topic as you like, but do stick to the theme.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tFirst of all, please allow me to show my deep sympathy for this &quot;China's son-in-law&quot; because it seems to be a little unfair to him. Like most of you, I also despise those people who claim that patronizing prostitutes is understandable and even legal. I don't know where their moral fibre goes, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/corroded\" target=\"_blank\">corroded</a> by their greedy for wealth and right? So why did I say it's unfair? The reason why Huang Haibo event caused such an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/uproar\" target=\"_blank\">uproar</a> lies in the title &quot;China's son-in-law&quot;, which is given by us TV viewers. Just as the old saying goes, never judge a person by his appearance. What we're really familiar with about Mr. Huang is only those figures he acted according to the script. There's no doubt that Mr. Huang will bear the corresponding law responsibility and undergo a tough time in his acting career. But at the same time, the question is proposed whether or not those celebrities' privacy should be excessively revealed by the authority and the media.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Prostitution\" target=\"_blank\">Prostitution</a> may be the world&rsquo;s most ancient profession. The urge of an adult man is so strong that an innocent woman may fall victim to the animal desire. In China&rsquo;s thousands of years&rsquo; history, prostitution always was legal and even some famous prostitutes left some noble deeds along the great man in the process of big era. But since the communist party&rsquo;s takeover in 1949, prostitution had become illegal. When an ordinary people wanted to have <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/out-of-wedlock\" target=\"_blank\">out-of-wedlock</a> sex, he had to venture himself in prison or even death sentence. (The <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/hierarchy\" target=\"_blank\">hierarchy</a> at that time can enjoy the companionship of the young girls in the culture <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/troupe\" target=\"_blank\">troupes</a>.) Now, the protestant propaganda of the communist party has been swept into the trash can and people&rsquo;s mind is more and more liberated, legalizing the prostitution once again emerges as a hot topic in the debate in Chinese social life. I, who never patronized prostitutes before, <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/adamantly\" target=\"_blank\">adamantly</a> stand in favor of it. DongGuan(东莞) which got its fame by a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/crackdown\" target=\"_blank\">crackdown</a> several months ago, should be a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/lighthouse\" target=\"_blank\">lighthouse</a> and sex capital of China. &nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/914620/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p706491/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p706491\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707208/\">囧研究 男人更愿帮助穿高跟鞋的女性</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706698/\">看懂《星际穿越》 必须了解的物理知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706993/\">他杀！ 梵高之死的惊人真相</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706765/\">“Fuck”的正确使用方法  图文并茂！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707158/\">萌娃来袭 粉丝过万 灰姑娘变公主</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707307/\">不男不女 波兰奇葩理由封杀小熊维尼</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707312/\">别人家的护照 挪威极光护照美如画</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p707342/\">全球幸福指数排名 越南第二中国60</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p706877/\">一见不钟情 沙特新郎看到妻子就离婚</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
